==English==
===Etymology===
contracted form of al be it, "even if it be so that" 
===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ɔːlˈbiːɪt/
===Conjunction===
'''albeit'''
# [[although]]; [[even though]]
# [[but]]
#:''He has a very good idea, '''albeit''' a strange one.''

